curl_init()

	initializes a new session and return a cURL handle

curl_setopt()

	sets option on cURL handle

curl_exec()

	execute cURL session
	OBS: should be called after curl_init() and curl_setopt()


------cURL options--------------------------------

CURLOPT_POST

	normal HTML POST

CURLOPT_POSTFIELDS

	the full data to POST

CURLOPT_PUT

	normal HTTP file PUT
